><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vqz1665702709424.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vqz1665702709424.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vqz1665702709424.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vqz1665702709424\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Menu\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Menu is a Development Object that defines a Uniface menu bar, dropdown menu, or pop-up menu for a desktop application. It is cannot be used in web applications.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vqz1665702709424__section_w485ab1b5b1_w486ab1b5_w487ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vqz1665702709424__section_w488ab1b5b3_w489ab1b5_w490ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d421750e56\">\n                     \n Characteristics\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vqz1665702709424__table_d10691e1_d10692e1_d10693e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vqz1665702709424__table_d10691e1_d10692e1_d10693e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vqz1665702709424__table_d10691e1_d10692e1_d10693e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqz1665702709424__table_d10691e1_d10692e1_d10693e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqz1665702709424__table_d10691e1_d10692e1_d10693e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">men</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqz1665702709424__table_d10691e1_d10692e1_d10693e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqz1665702709424__table_d10691e1_d10692e1_d10693e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqz1665702709424__table_d10691e1_d10692e1_d10693e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqz1665702709424__table_d10691e1_d10692e1_d10693e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Menu Library</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqz1665702709424__table_d10691e1_d10692e1_d10693e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqz1665702709424__table_d10691e1_d10692e1_d10693e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqz1665702709424__table_d10691e1_d10692e1_d10693e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqz1665702709424__table_d10691e1_d10692e1_d10693e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqz1665702709424__table_d10691e1_d10692e1_d10693e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqz1665702709424__table_d10691e1_d10692e1_d10693e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqz1665702709424__table_d10691e1_d10692e1_d10693e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqz1665702709424__table_d10691e1_d10692e1_d10693e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">MenuName</var>@<var class=\"keyword varname\">LibraryName</var>@<var class=\"keyword varname\">Language</var>.men</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqz1665702709424__table_d10691e1_d10692e1_d10693e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqz1665702709424__table_d10691e1_d10692e1_d10693e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">lib:<var class=\"keyword varname\">LibraryName.Language</var>:men:<var class=\"keyword varname\">MenuName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vqz1665702709424__section_w491ab1b5b5_w492ab1b5_w493ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d421750e258\">\n                     \n Specialization\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vqz1665702709424__p_d96248e1_d96249e1_d96250e1\">Uniface Menu specializes Development Object in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vqz1665702709424__li_d38996e1_d38997e1_d38998e1\">It has a Menu Library as parent. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vqz1665702709424__li_d38999e1_d39000e1_d39001e1\">It does not have child development objects. </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"vqz1665702709424__note_w497ab1b5b5b7_w498ab1b5b5_w499ab1b5_w500ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> It is possible to implement menus using other mechanisms, such as tabs, popup windows, and contained forms.</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616581\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616581\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Menu Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Menu A Menu is a Development Object that defines a Uniface menu bar, dropdown menu, or pop-up menu for a desktop application. It is cannot be used in web applications. Characteristics Characteristics Object type code: men Main Development Object? No Part of: Menu Library Contains: Property , Code Container Generalization: Development Object Specializations: — Compilation Output: MenuName @ LibraryName @ Language .men URI format: lib: LibraryName.Language :men: MenuName Specialization Uniface Menu specializes Development Object in the following ways: It has a Menu Library as parent. It does not have child development objects. Note: It is possible to implement menus using other mechanisms, such as tabs, popup windows, and contained forms. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}